Package: GADGET
Title: Gaussian Process Approximations for Designing Experiments
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Isaac", "Michaud", email = "ijmichau@ncsu.edu",role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Brian", "Weaver", role = c("aut")),
             person("Brian", "Williams", role = c("aut")))
Description: Computes near-optimal Bayesian experimental designs with Gaussian processes optimization following the algorithm presented by Weaver et al. (2016) <doi:10.1214/15-BA945> for either physical or sequential computer experiments.
License: GPL-3 
